# Router Buffering

NAME
    ./router

SYNOPSYS
    ./router [OPTION]... [FILE]... (OPTIONAL)[BUFFER_SIZE] [BANDWIDTH]

DESCRIPTION
    This program simulates a router with a given bandwidth and buffer size

    -c 
        combine two files to run throught the buffer at the same time

RUN EXAMPLES
    sample run tests can be found in runfile found in this directory

AUTHOR
    Written by Karl Winkler

REPORTING BUGS
    Project github <https://github.com/KarlWinkler/Network-Projects/issues>
    with apropriate project name.    
